name: Bamboo Blend Cami Tops
description:
Introducing with our new eco collection of bamboo underthings 
for women, a basic yet fuctional driven Cami top.
Silky soft comfy fit great base layer design for cooler days without added bulk.

Lingerie style thin straps available in white, form fit, longer length 95% bamboo 5% spandex
*Very stretchy fabric*

Machine washable, cold, tumble low heat or line dry

Additional colors available soon!

name: Basic Stain Proof Bikini
description:
Stain resistant layers of leak proof liners technology inspired 
Classic fit latex elastic trim panties. 
Slightly higher sides low raise, elastic trim adds extra bum coverage no riding up full cut style. 

Bamboo is hygienic, antifungal, more breathable than cotton, lightweight throughout skin stays cool and dry withstands multiple machine washings. 
Base: 95% Bamboo Viscose, 5% Lycra

Moisture wicked micropolyester liners
Inner lining is a high tech moisture wicking polymer providing leak resistant layers of soft absorbent leak free barrier protection through-out.

Wetness will not pass through to outer garment due to special stay dry fabric. 
Offering a practical option for disposable products. 

*These fabrics are very stretchy if in doubt ORDER SMALLER size

Garment care: Machine washable cold turn inside out, tumble dry low heat or line dry
